name: The "Other" Space Invaders collection-salmon pink
description:
Make a bold statement with this colorful handmade necklace from my collection: The "other" Space Invaders.

All the necklaces in this collection are short and worn close to the neckline as in the photo of sky blue necklace. If you wish a specific design but a different yarn color from what you see, ask away!I can do custom orders!

For more photos check my page www.facebook.com/vallistic and if you like it press the like button!

Materials: plastic beads, metal findings, yarn
Length: Approx. 46cm but it also has extender chain

- All my items come gift-wrapped.
- I ship internationally.
